@startuml 1.6 User edits his profile (user side and server side)
actor User
participant IHMMain
participant Data
participant Communication
actor Server 

User ->> IHMMain++: Modifie le profil



 
IHMMain -> Data++: updateUser(user: User)
Data -> Communication++: updateUser(user: User)

Communication ->> Server++: updateUser(user: User)
Communication --> Data: void | Exception

deactivate Server
deactivate Communication

Data --> IHMMain: void | Exception

deactivate Data
deactivate IHMMain
    

@enduml
